{"tid":219732,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"《殺手榜》","createTime":"2017-04-27T11:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T17:41:46.000Z","uid":108643,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c75f3e4e6aa0c8a80c860facd5fe91aea4c379","tid":219732,"uid":108643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:59:32.000Z","msg":"人命有價。<br />\n<br />\n每條人命，都有個價。<br />\n<br />\n有人會稱我們為人間中的「死神」，因為是生是死，都出自我們一念之間。<br />\n<br />\n香港之大，要去何處尋覓殺手？<br />\n<br />\n我會說，當你真正窮途末路必需要我們出手時‧‧‧‧‧‧<br />\n<br />\n你自然會尋得著。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n殺手榜<br />\n────────────────────────"},{"pid":"a3842c3e1bfc770e956103c049fec75985182332","tid":219732,"uid":108643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:59:56.000Z","msg":"序章──<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「喂！」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「喂！！」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「喂！！！」</span><br />\n<br />\n「&hellip;！？」我猛地睜開了眼睛，廚房裡的炒菜聲、怨罵聲，又頻頻傳入耳中。<br />\n<br />\n「我叫你呀！」老闆在一旁大聲咒罵，生怕我聽不到似的：「叫你返工定發夢啊！你睇下你炒依碟牛河&hellip;炒撚到屎咁叫啲客點食啊？」<br />\n<br />\n我低頭一望鍋裡的乾炒牛河，的確是被我體無完膚地破壞了。<br />\n<br />\n「唉～醒目啲啦！屌你老母！！加媽嗲啦仆街！！！」老闆每天循例的惡罵惡語，我早已經習慣。<br />\n<br />\n老闆離開後，耳根清靜不少，我又繼續專注在眼前的乾炒牛河上。已經轉了數十多份工，我不想再過著不穩的生活。<br />\n<br />\n「哈哈哈，o靚仔，你日日俾個條友罵都無反應咁嘅～？」一旁負責處理煲鍋飯的師傅徐徐笑道：「我哋啲廚房佬出名好爆嫁喎，如果佢咁樣對住我屌多兩屌&hellip;睇下佢個頭會唔會流血。」<br />\n<br />\n我專注在鍋子上，加上油煎炒炸聲太大，沒太聽到他在說什麼。而且他們好像都喜歡周杰倫，總是在廚房內播放著《青花瓷》一曲，然後淡淡哼唱。<br />\n<br />\n每天如是，過著如此重覆又反覆的生活。"},{"pid":"4704728337839ac9e71719005b8ca86df2d1342f","tid":219732,"uid":108643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:00:41.000Z","msg":"上班下班行的是同一條路、見的都是同一伙人、做的都是同一件事，週而復始只為著那一天的到來&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「唔該&hellip;要&hellip;&hellip;要一碟乾炒豬肉公仔麵&hellip;走豬肉&hellip;加辣，落蔥花同蒜頭，仲有加花生&hellip;&hellip;」外面一位戴住口罩、鴨子帽及太陽眼鏡的一位女士，向侍應落單。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n侍應帶著愕然的表情，寫著她要的東西，便走入廚房放下單子：「哇&hellip;出面有條八婆玩嘢&hellip;花生配公仔麵&hellip;&hellip;你哋自己睇住嚟炒。」說畢，就轉身離開。<br />\n<br />\n聽到此處，我眼神不禁一銳，就接過單子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「少見喎，自動自覺拎嘢嚟炒。」早已是地中海年紀的大廚對我呵呵一笑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我照著單子上所寫的去炒麵，順便把乾炒公仔麵送出去給那位客人，就徑自走到去中菜館外的後巷，抽上根煙放鬆一下。從口中吐出的淡薄煙霧，形態比紙更為脆弱，卻更加逍遙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不久，餐館通往後巷的門被慢慢地推開，剛才點了乾炒公仔麵走豬肉的那位女客人，她走了出來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原本看似有些膽怯的她望一望我，定了定神，然後問：「你&hellip;你係咪&hellip;人&hellip;人間&hellip;兵器&hellip;&hellip;」她聲音既小又顫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我斜瞪了她一眼，沒有回答，繼續望前、吐煙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我&hellip;我都係&hellip;&hellip;逼不得已&hellip;先&hellip;&hellip;先要搵你&hellip;原本只&hellip;只係想試一試&hellip;估唔到&hellip;&hellip;係真&hellip;」她繼續說。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這女人廢話很多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我&hellip;我叫BOBO&hellip;」她索性卸下太陽眼鏡與口罩，一副清緻的容貌頓時顯現於眼前：「我想&hellip;&hellip;拜托你殺一個人。」"},{"pid":"73838ce2cac7e58baa0ae338cc91b333f2ec40d6","tid":219732,"uid":108643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:06:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第一章──退隱的高手</div></strong><br />\n<br />\n我不屑地盯她一眼，就打算返回廚房工作。<br />\n<br />\n「等陣啊&hellip;」她卻想要伸手搭住我的膊頭，強烈的壓迫感之下，我立即轉身捉住其腕，再用力一扭！<br />\n<br />\n「呀&hellip;！！」她尖聲痛叫了一下，淚水徐徐而下：「求&hellip;求你&hellip;求下你&hellip;&hellip;我&hellip;我爸爸&hellip;我爸爸佢&hellip;&hellip;走咗&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n我停下來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她按著應該已經中度肌骨扭傷的手腕，忍住痛說：「佢&hellip;佢死之前&hellip;叫我嚟依到&hellip;搵你&hellip;話你可以將我&hellip;&hellip;拯救&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n妳父親？我回頭一望那女孩子的臉，想從她的輪廓中猜一下她父親是何方人物。因為在殺手圈中認識我的人只有寥寥數個，而且我已經退隱了一段日子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乾炒豬肉公仔麵、走豬肉、加辣、落蔥花、蒜頭，還有花生&hellip;&hellip;我大概有些印象了，從前有個客人在聘請我去殺人之前，都會有個簡短的見面談話，而這種吃法&hellip;應該就是他了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可是，我從來不會去記住別人的名字。"},{"pid":"447c2ec045aa43da23d1408efa39ace437221142","tid":219732,"uid":51516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:47:34.000Z","msg":"唔出喇？"},{"pid":"e76c9cf0b41ef3fb40e1c15da46d244516939998","tid":219732,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:59:46.000Z","msg":"棄故？"},{"pid":"e737f1b0518ef3399c0e6ff4ddb25725661f8773","tid":219732,"uid":21200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:02:10.000Z","msg":"墨巴個朋友 出文啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30111bacb2e8441203d4df43484e694103c21186","tid":219732,"uid":74455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:11:40.000Z","msg":"呢邊都想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14418ddd915b66eff76984827ca54c62616a4a56","tid":219732,"uid":98704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:45:09.000Z","msg":"樓主快d出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf71a688b60e65cfcd47f9228e5424f7a63ee6f3","tid":219732,"uid":16108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:48:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0e7b15dc9af414b3c812a344eb525e10480bbbfc","tid":219732,"uid":51755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T15:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8865f193a40743fd7a2ab524e1cd49b171386ac4","tid":219732,"uid":76320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:54:35.000Z","msg":"期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32e499c8240ab4f1b80dcdb475492a468c0d2ca","tid":219732,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:57:14.000Z","msg":"默巴快d黎騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4e925cfcc633543f65fd8375227474357cb5c0","tid":219732,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>墨巴快d黎騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b918d0b37d269be431d59e609fe7aded13c07fd5","tid":219732,"uid":115908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"呢個故好似都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268e549efb3235402de92527622a160ccd27f63d","tid":219732,"uid":2860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:39:27.000Z","msg":"墨巴個朋友點解唔再出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fc7bf3638ea0e392597f2451204b406a9380f5","tid":219732,"uid":98704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:06:00.000Z","msg":"墨巴快d理下呢邊個故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95842f77782458294ed1f17cf662790ade339470","tid":219732,"uid":51516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T22:57:41.000Z","msg":"好想睇"},{"pid":"20a846d2c4347a2e063e2fb3f2c0f02fb18a3856","tid":219732,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T23:00:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"444e14964292e7a35930abed468bed19639f09cc","tid":219732,"uid":98704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T16:36:01.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08df400f16a9f518c3feba0fea39d0addcb320a7","tid":219732,"uid":38888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6fcf1429accc5eb389dc04eb40d2b7ae749b16","tid":219732,"uid":52814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:32:24.000Z","msg":"題材好有趣 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8e74c81226ac059b4280c56b712e8161abc76d","tid":219732,"uid":36658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T18:38:00.000Z","msg":"文呢屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2441a609dfecf6ba5c2b3cac5a164247da50ef31","tid":219732,"uid":43901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T18:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7359923493b0eb324cfa1b72a9df6e71857bfc1","tid":219732,"uid":7612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T18:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"}]}